sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant M as Middleware
    participant R as Router
    participant H as Handler
    participant S as Service
    participant D as Database

    C->>M: HTTP Request
    activate M
    M->>M: Process Request
    M->>R: Route Request
    activate R
    R->>H: Match Handler
    activate H
    H->>S: Call Service
    activate S
    S->>D: Query Data
    activate D
    D-->>S: Return Data
    deactivate D
    S-->>H: Return Result
    deactivate S
    H-->>R: Format Response
    deactivate H
    R-->>M: Return Response
    deactivate R
    M->>M: Process Response
    M-->>C: HTTP Response
    deactivate M
